03:33.952 --> 03:39.956
We're all doing kickstands...

03:39.958 --> 03:43.826
One of my best friends...

03:57.874 --> 03:59.508
Hey, can I get a beer?

03:59.510 --> 04:01.711
Uh, yeah sure.

04:02.980 --> 04:05.715
Seth did you want it in your hands?

04:05.717 --> 04:09.318
Umm, is there the option for a cup, or?

04:09.320 --> 04:13.589
I mean, we had cups...

04:13.591 --> 04:16.659
Um... Well where's your cup?

04:16.661 --> 04:20.463
I'm just in charge of
distribution for tonight.

04:20.464 --> 04:23.566
The responsible one. Respect.

04:23.568 --> 04:25.534
Irregardless, it's my lot in life.

04:25.536 --> 04:28.271
Ah, but irregardless means regardless,

04:28.273 --> 04:30.906
and there's no such thing as the former.

04:30.908 --> 04:35.678
Ahahahah, holy shit. Uh, impressive. Hi.

04:35.680 --> 04:36.412
Hi.

04:36.414 --> 04:36.946
Seth.

04:36.948 --> 04:36.946
Em.

04:36.948 --> 04:40.850
Em... Is that short for Emily?

04:40.852 --> 04:45.788
Normal length for em, actually.

04:45.790 --> 04:45.788
This is, um,

04:45.790 --> 04:50.626
interesting music for a
rite of passage party.

04:50.628 --> 04:53.029
