01:12:48.836 --> 01:12:53.105
Can I have a room? Please?

01:15:01.100 --> 01:15:02.934
Daddy?

01:15:04.872 --> 01:15:07.939
It's an rfid chip.

01:15:07.941 --> 01:15:11.610
